 could be included, but for something like getMethod, it looks like I need the metadata for the public method getInstance(Object). The class metadata might be comprehensive. I wonder if this qualifies as \"normal public API.\" Since ItsUtils.fillList is a public generic method that uses getInstance, would that provide the necessary coverage, or does it focus more on library metadata rather than user-defined helpers? It’s a bit tricky!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_046dc510cb1c89d0016a25ce2dfde0819591d1ca837e99efa9\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqJc5I7e5L7wZe00GkiUY2X3XN9AvAPdQmTJRTlAXr_Zk3N_6IWl1R6KCe-5STXca2SUv4wSubKASUArs8lz-mtDBUD9m0E1GGz2SjoDMj2a3sCdENt34L21TEswB7JaHHl5-3www9ag0H5aIUcoRwO8f6wyLeIUE7ewDB7bhmYH5p1Kc8S_S0DGpDeHREhJcJ4Z5ohek7oTr2GvTj9AC86o6oZvii8AM22Ylepj5FsZJQLU3xv_SxesbNZsDsbDwcsO-7EKE2Z2sKg3JOqRP4BfcMwAlkIK2RvM0hF6-sTxXeQtqfYE6yb7bC6Ry5dXzAyqL_t4xlhGTmcb2GCmWvluPlGkEFl45_1YHTzcN3lWrg_XBhUzlBcj55V0A49CMBjMDfcLbRBdsHtLQ9o7NtOnXGVTOFK4E95NQ_234ICk_nntnWO7CfIDjJ0pEx8f__1MEklaTGMQHWROIcc8q2j3yjOCavJZFFHUjoNRdwZoctpr_wemXL_Wtx1okKpoossTHdjek4TKNRqnNMhj_mM5g5oS8zqmjaRbPAe8F-eNjBwz2DACox-vqJW1NCU5DVvSua6ycKePiV3y3aTOkZsZyg4qk9zqVmD9Oj6MApX60VXiDF6GoErnU0WmJnULiqYRE3Vh09ZOOgo7yqhXD_9GGfNCzk-mndOXG76c6sh6U792m66Zq9-D5ib6Z5T1V7uOcDbnPNngvJbIEK1kMtQf1Z_6byY5a3yphWxgLb2GSefuNvSx6A_0HDzD6F4ANESC0Os-x1keY20k-MWbnaiD-ej21jnMPIJXXL22ySSybvJXmZkqQ-SSPvMjNEQc8FCYUkDCc9N6HwBOfjvxtoQxzo6A7GqqH7pQoaGmXLhGqVRGPkUd32h08UdYQC8AF_wDZEyI1TvuyArewPEgu4vjr8osx0Ek8bHFlSKzhzZGlh-xHOztFp6ZJhlrCXXA0JKkE9c2ETH9KRfM7GkgXOZoichFLN4IWqAfSJxsLJnl779VltjJ2LQKaPlJ5hWLd4kljRnCEyhAqbDU86ForsmMvSOcIHAhg-mGBuJs3kDWAz8ROxWJBvMOkuAh1iYE4vByUmwIPyvufmsCw6Nd84rHQRCgfDLDc130t2iVZE1TNbMcxvg-iU3YXhnwrARYC77F5-4X4KXGic_WDm3G5gRnFMT7kk4H7ybnL2Vv8NhcJIqKSDFjZgRIgdG3xYYCdZ_FZBMnistLOP_HGixu-dKFTb-iQ0AZUhyCAxQrqb8bcEVX0-CS9bYoejoDCWFsj-1Q0VqaD6cT2xmlUEXSZFxmdQmuWeyEJcxFb8BorPDR55YpwZnXQh4MFTjnyYH76zrkttJ4NjtRuGYntVDSKvV8uLvRwtOrRwv3KMDbpNTLES6qN34PZmk-6RN